Module edu.wgu.tmaama
Package edu.wgu.tmaama.db.Appointment.model

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
edu.wgu.tmaama.db.Appointment.model.Appointment
public class Appointment extends Object
Appointment model class. Extra fields include localStart and localEnd for easier time displaying data in user's local time.
